                    <physDesc>
                        <objectDesc>
                            <supportDesc>
                                <support>
                                    <p>A stele or cippus with a rounded upper edge, of a dark grey limestone. Intact on the left, and on the left lower edge and probably the upper left edge also; but broken/damaged on the right upper and lower parts. The face is partly flaked off the surface, and a natural flaw runs vertically across the face of the stone also.</p>
                                    <material ana="#material.stone.limestone" ref="http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/material/lod/66.html">limestone</material>
                                    <objectType ana="#object.stele" ref="http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/objtyp/lod/250">stele</objectType>
